<br>
(Skill + level)/400<br>
<br>
Now, in that scenario, how much difference is there between level 61 and level 62?  The answer is &quot;Not a whole helluva lot&quot;  Skill is the main variable, because it's larger and goes up in larger increments..and it also stops going up post 60.  If all equations in EQ use a formula similar to that, like lets say your chance to hit a mob is ==<br>
<br>
(Offense + weapon skill + level) - (mob ac + mob level)/ some variable<br>
<br>
